snippet.title: Ilysia | Kickstarter Trailer |Team 21 Studio, LLC
snippet.description:
We did it! Ilysia has finally come to Kickstarter! This is our chance to finally make Ilysia happen, you can back us at the following link: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/team21studio/ilysia-experience-the-glory-days-of-mmorpgs-again-in-vr

Please share this link everywhere you can to help spread awareness of Ilysia!

A MASSIVE thank you to our entire community for all your continued support, we wouldn't be here without you!

Ilysia Website: https://ilysiavr.com/

Ilysia Discord: https://discord.gg/ilysia
